productBaseInfoV1.title: Benro PP1 PocketPod Tripod Kit(Black, Supports Up to 1500 g)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The PocketPod Table Top Tripod is the perfect take-everywhere support. Benro's PocketPod can be used as a tabletop tripod as well as a handgrip for smartphones, GoPro or DSLR cameras. Small enough to fit in your pocket, the PocketPod is made of high quality plastic with non-slip rubber feet and an all-metal ball. The integrated ball head allows camera positions from horizontal to vertical and can be securely locked in any position with a quick twist of the locking ring. Each leg has two grooves for a more comfortable and secure grip when using as a handgrip. The PocketPod supports up to 3.3 pounds while weighing only 5.6 ounces (.35 lb.). Its built-in ball head has a 1/4"-20 camera screw and a unique design that allows adjustments and locking with a single twist of the locking ring The Benro PP1 PocketPod Tabletop Tripod holds any compact camera or other equipment with a 1/4"-20 threaded mount that weighs up to 3.3 lb. The tripod has a maximum height of 5.3", and when folded up it can also be used as a handheld stabilizer which measures 6.9" long. The PP1's one-section legs have rubber feet for added friction on smooth surfaces, and its built-in ball head has a ring lock to control the ball's movement. productBaseInfoV1.title: Benro A2980F(Supports Up to 10000 g)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Besides being an essential camera accessory, tripod helps change the overall quality of a picture. They also assist in fine tuning images to make them well-composed, sharp and impeccable. Built under the Versatile Transformer Tripod Series from Benro, the Benro A2980F camera trivet incorporates latest technologies to offer an exceptional operating performance. Fused with Magnesium Alloy castings, this tripod reduces vibration and is fused with a double surface protection. Weighing 2110 g, the Benro A2980F tripod is capable of mounting equipment weighing up to 10000 g. Besides this, the adjustable leg angles allow for easy setting up of the tripod. Each leg could be independently set to 24 degree, 55 degree or 80 degree leg angle.  Body On folding the Benro A2980F camera trivet, it measures a length of 560 mm, thus making it compact to carry during extensive photographic expeditions. To enable you to shoot images from various angles, this tripod comes with a maximum operating height of 1730 mm and a normal operating height of 1365 mm. You could further minimize the trivet to a lowest operating height of up to 390 mm. Adding to the comfort, the four leg sections of the Benro A2980F tripod use advanced 1.2 mm thick aluminium tubing which maximizes the strength of the tripod while usage. Besides this, the rubber feet provide a firm grip on rough and slippery terrains. These removable screw-on rubber feet can be interchanged with spiked feet depending upon the surface of the shooting location. The maximum diameter of this Benro tripod is 29 mm and the minimum diameter is 18.5 mm. Features The embedded center column of the Benro A2980F trivet allows for an overall alteration of the height of the apparatus while shooting. The patented column locking set knobs come with a unique advantage of providing both horizontal and vertical center column positioning. Integrated with a flip style leg section locking system, you could be assured of a smooth, secure and easy extension of the legs. Designed to meet the growing demands of the innovative photographers of today, the Benro A2980F tripod makes provision for extra low angled shooting. The legs of this trivet also consist of closed foam grip which is made from Nitrile Butadiene Rubber for extra firm control and is resistant to cold, making it perfect for use even in extremely cold weather conditions. Lightweight in nature, setting up this Benro A2980F tripod is swift and simple.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Bushnell 158042  Binoculars(8 x , Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Spend enough time on the water, and your equipment will spend some time in it. That's why Bushnell had the foresight to build the H20 series of binoculars, which are O-ring-sealed and nitrogen-purged to complete lock out moisture should you spill water on the housing, take your binoculars overboard, or simply run into foul weather along the way. The H20 binoculars feature rubber armoring with textured pads to give you a sturdy grip in slippery situations. More significantly, the binocular's multicoated optics and premium-quality Bak-4 prisms maximize light transmission and image clarity, so you can enjoy a clear view of the Orcas in the distance or the fast-approaching coastline. You'll quickly see how a little planning on Bushnell's part goes a long way in magnifying your adventures on or around the water. Other features include twist-up eyecups, a large center focus knob for easy, precise adjustments, and a long eye relief.

productBaseInfoV1.title: DigiFlip Wizard CB001  Camera Bag(Blue)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: If you are looking for a camera backpack that will effectively carry and protect your photography gear while still not burning a hole in your pocket, you need to look no further. The DigiFlip Wizard CB001 is a DSLR camera backpack from the house of Flipkart. The main compartment of this backpack can hold a DSLR camera with attached lens along with 2 - 3 lenses or flashes and smaller accessories. The DigiFlip Wizard can also comfortably hold chargers, memory cards, cables, mobile phones, mp3 players and other such small accessories in the secondary compartment. This DigiFlip Wizard backpack has adjustable and padded shoulder straps that are comfortable to carry on long distances. The hip strap enables you to comfortably carry this backpack even when fully loaded. The outer body of this DigiFlip backpack has a sleek and streamlined design. The exterior is made of water repellent 1680D polyester while the interior is made of padded tricot providing great protection to your photography gear. This backpack has a padded mesh backpad which provides adequate lumbar support. The velcro dividers are fully adjustable, letting you customize the space in the main compartment of your bag as you wish. The two additional pockets below the flap provide space for more accessories and can even carry small point-and-shoot cameras.

productBaseInfoV1.title: NIKON Action VII 7-15X35 CF Zoom  Binoculars(,)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Enjoy the beauty of watching birds and wild animals in their natural habitat with the Nikon Action VII 7-15X35 CF Zoom Binoculars. You can expect bright and clear images with these binoculars as they are equipped with high-quality porro prisms. The binoculars can be used for a variety of outdoor activities like bird-watching, hiking, mountaineering and backpack tours.  The binoculars have a magnification up to 15x. You can enjoy bright and detailed images by getting up to 15 times closer to the subject. This feature is helpful when you are tracking small birds in an open arena as you can quickly zoom in to the required level and view your subject. The images remain stable and clear even when fully magnified. Body The Nikon Action binoculars have a sleek and sophisticated finish. The binoculars have rubber armoring that provides superior grip and comfort even during long hours of viewing sessions. The binoculars have a center focus that is located between the 2 viewing barrels, while the diopter adjustment lies on the right eyepiece. The Nikon binoculars have soft eyecups that are comfortable on the eyes. For those who wear glasses, the eyecups can be folded down to view the entire field of view, without straining your eyes. The binoculars are an ideal companion for long mountain trekking trips as they are shock resistant. The feature is useful when you are indulged in intense viewing sessions as you need not worry about the maintenance of your binoculars. The Nikon Action binoculars have the dimensions of 182 mm X 138 mm in width and depth, respectively. You can easily pack these binoculars into a backpack or a travel bag as they weigh just 805 g. Performance The Nikon binoculars have a variable zoom of 7x to 15x. The wide zoom range lets you easily focus onto a subject to produce clear, focused visuals. You can quickly change the power settings without any hassle. The zooming mechanism is smooth for any distance, no matter how near or far it is. The Nikon Action CF has a 35 mm objective lens. The large diameter of the lens assists in effective transmission of light within the binoculars, letting you enjoy sharp, contrast-rich images. With an exit pupil of 5 mm, the Nikon Action can be used from dawn to dusk as it can produce clear images even under dimply-lit environments. With this feature available, you can carry these binoculars to museums and art exhibitions. The Nikon binoculars have a center focus with diopter adjustment. The center focus is easy to adjust and produces bright and steady visuals. To further fine-tune the focus, you can use the diopter adjustment to correct the eye difference and enjoy high-quality visuals. The Action CF binoculars have a close focus measuring 11 m. This feature helps you to zoom in from the closest to the farthest distances, without any difficulty. The Nikon Action has an eye relief of 8.7 mm that assists in strain-less viewing of the entire field of view. You can effortlessly pan across wide environments with these binoculars as they have a 5.5° angle of view. This makes it easy to track fast moving such as birds and animals in the wild. The Nikon Action CF has multi-coated lenses and prisms. The coatings add sharpness, contrast and natural definition of the images. The coatings also assist in eliminating reflections and deflecting harsh glare of the sun. If you indulge in long hours of viewing sessions, you can easily attach these binoculars to a tripod as they are tripod mountable. The attachment will provide you with clear and shake-free visuals, letting you enjoy your favourite hobby without straining your hands. Buying Guide Animals and birds tend to move very fast in wide environments. One moment they can be in front of you and the next moment they can be gone before a blink of an eye. While viewing fast moving subjects, a pair of binoculars with variable zoom is necessary so that you don’t lose track of your subject. The Nikon Action VII 7-15X35 CF Zoom Binoculars offer variable zoom and many more features that can make your every trip a memorable one, making them a truly versatile product to own. Along with the above mentioned uses, these binoculars can also be used for camping and watching spectator sports.

With the Celestron UpClose you can experience all this and more. With a large magnification of 8x, the UpClose binoculars can take you 8 times closer to the subject you zoom in on, letting you enjoy high-quality visuals. The quality of the image-in-view does not differ even when fully magnified. Body The full-size binoculars have a rubber covered body. The smooth rubber body provides good grip and is comfortable to hold even during extended sessions of viewing. The binoculars have a knurled center focus that is located between the 2 viewing barrels, along with the diopter adjustment that is available on the right eyepiece. The UpClose binoculars are weather-resistant. You can use them on warm April days or rain-filled July afternoons, the binoculars will provide you with the same satisfactory performance as always. The Celestron binoculars weigh 680.39 g and can be easily carried around in your back pack or travel bag. Performance The Celestron UpClose has an objective lens measuring 40 mm.  The large diameter of the lens gathers more light and focuses them on the eyepiece lens, letting you enjoy sharp quality images. Dim-lit environments will not be a concern with these binoculars as they have an exit pupil of 5 mm, helping you to see visuals clearly in events like musical concerts or exhibitions. The UpClose binoculars have a center focus with a diopter adjustment. You can adjust the center focus to precisely close in on your subject. For additional fine tuning of the focus, you can use the diopter adjustment available on the right eye piece. The close focus measures 4.88 m and refers to the closest distance through which you can adjust your focus onto a subject, extending to infinity. With an eye relief of 12 mm, the Celestron UpClose is useful for glass wearers as they can view the entire field of view, without straining their eyes. The lenses of the UpClose binoculars are fully coated and help in enhancing the sharpness and contrast of all the visuals you see. The coatings also help in eliminating reflections and reducing glare from the sun. The Celestron UpClose 8 x 40 binoculars offer an angle of view of 8.2°, letting you to effortlessly pan the binoculars across wide environments. This feature is very helpful when you are viewing quick moving subjects such as birds or animals in the wild. You can enjoy shake free visuals for hours with these binoculars as they are tripod mountable. Just attach these with a stable tripod to avoid strain to your hands and body and enjoy your favourite activities without any hassle. Buying Guide If you want a sturdy pair of binoculars that can be used for an array of activities, the Celestron Upclose 8 x 40 binoculars are the answer for you. With a water resistant body and a large angle of view, these binoculars promise reliable performance every time.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Think Tank Urban Disguise 50 Classic  Camera Bag(Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Think Tank Urban Disguise 50 Classic is a camera shoulder bag that is designed to be stylish while being a fully functional option for the traveling photographer. This bag is crafted with genuine leather accents and panels, which contribute to a tasteful look that evokes the appearance of a well-designed briefcase.A wide-mouth opening at the top and reinforced dividers that ensure that gear is held towards the opening make it easy to store and remove items from this bag. The Urban Disguise 50 Classic can fit one to two gripped or standard DSLRs with lenses attached, plus one to four additional lenses, a tablet and up to a 15.4" widescreen laptop. An expansion zipper increases the depth to fit a gripped DSLR along with an attached zoom lens.Aside from being able to comfortably hold photo gear, plus a laptop or tablet, the bag's zippered front pocket organizer provides storage for pens, business cards, keys, and small electronics. To accommodate a water bottle, strobe unit, or a small umbrella, stretchable side pockets are also included. When accessing the main compartment or the front pocket organizer, sound silencers dampen noise from the front flap's touch-tab closures so that discretion can be maintained in quiet environments. For security, the zippers on the camera and laptop compartments can accommodate a lock. Particularly useful during travel are built-in pass-throughs for both the shoulder strap and the bag itself that enable piggy-backing on a rolling case. Nylon construction throughout the bag and a polyurethane-coated bottom provide a high degree of built-in weather resistance, and a seam-sealed rain cover is included for even more protection from the elements should the need arise. The Urban Disguise 50 Classic can be carried several ways. A leather-wrapped dual handle provides a comfortable grip and the included shoulder strap is padded. For particularly heavy loads, the separately-sold Think Tank Shoulder Harness V2.0 can be used to more evenly distribute the weight.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Think Tank Suburban Disguise 10  Camera Bag(Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Think Tank Sub Urban Disguise 10 Shoulder Bag features a compact design to hold your DSLR with 2 or 3 small zooms or prime lenses. It can also hold three pro-sized flashes with extra room for radio triggers/receivers.The bag contains a zippered front flap that opens away from your body. This not only provides rapid access to your gear but serves as a security feature since no one will be able to see inside the bag. Your camera is held facing down ready to be removed and used. There are plenty of pockets for accessories. The front organizer flap has enough room for your smartphone, memory cards, pens and similar sized items. The front flap contains a pocket underneath in which you can store batteries, maps or a camera manual. The zippered mesh pocket in the lid is sized to hold the included rain cover. Side stretch pockets are provided to hold water bottles. The pocket under the front flap can be latched open or touch fastened.The bag is made from 1680D ballistic polyester, 600D brushed polyester, 420D high-density nylon and coated on the underside with polyurethane for added water-resistance. The interior has removable closed-cell foam dividers with polyester and a Velex liner. For maximum protection outdoors, a rain cover is included. The zippers are all YKK. The bag also contains a handy lanyard for your keys. Carry the Disguise 10 by its adjustable shoulder strap or top carry handle.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Think Tank Retrospective Leather 7  Camera Bag(Grey With Brown Leather)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Think Tank Retrospective 7 Shoulder Bag is a shooter's bag. With enough space for your standard DSLR with a 24-70mm f/2.8 attached and a 70-200mm f/2.8 by its side, you'll also have enough room left over for your flash and accessories. Plus, there's a rear pocket large enough for your 10" tablet or 11" MacBook Air. The internal dividers can be configured to accommodate the gear you need that day. Inside, there are two hook and loop nylon pockets that can hold a flash or similar sized item. Outside, under the main flap is another pocket that can hold an additional DSLR body or accessories.The main flap is secured with hook and loop panels and all the zippers are durable YKK design. There's also a dual cross buckle on the front flap for added security. Think Tank's unique "Sound Silencers" - panels located under the main flap can be deployed to eliminate the "ripping" sound of the touch fasteners when you need to access the interior. This will come in handy when shooting in quiet venues such as court rooms, golf matches or public relations events.For business cards, there's a clear interior pocket for extra cards or your ID. An interior zippered organizer pocket can hold your filters, cleaning cloths and other small accessories. Pens, maps and even more stuff can be kept within a second interior storage pocket.Carrying the Retrospective 7 is easy with its adjustable canvas strap or removable top carry handle. The shoulder strap comes with a cushioned pad that can slid along the strap for optimum positioning. The strap is also supplied with patches of non-slip material to keep it stable while in use. For bad weather, the bag comes with a rain cover that covers the bag but exposes both the shoulder and carry strap.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Tiffen UV Protection Filter UV Filter(49 mm)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Tiffen UV Protection filter Film, as well as video, often exhibits a greater sensitivity to what is to us invisible, ultraviolet light. This is most often outdoors, especially at high altitudes, where the UV-absorbing atmosphere is thinner; and over long distances, such as marine scenes. It can show up as a bluish color cast with color film, or it can cause a low-contrast haze that diminishes details, especially when viewing far-away objects, in either color or black-and-white. Ultraviolet filters absorb UV light generally without affecting light in the visible region. Using a Tiffen UV Protector on your Digital HD DSLR While the UV Protection filter has served its purpose in the film era for many years it will still continue to be one of the most popular choices in accessories today. Digital cameras have blocks, auto correction and digital filters that combat the bluish color cast therefore making the UV Protection filter a simple protector for your lens to combat dirt, finger prints & that fateful knock or drop. Who are Tiffen? Tiffen has been a leading manufacturer and supplier of photographic filters and lens accessories for the consumer/professional imaging and the motion picture and broadcast television industries for 75 years. The company has a rich history of innovative product design, superior optical consistency and unparalleled quality. Tiffen has been recognized for its product and engineering excellence earning a Technical Achievement Award and a Scientific and Engineering Award from the Academy of Motion Picture Arts & Sciences, as well as an Emmy Award from the Academy of Television Arts and Sciences. Features ? Low profile black ring ? Basic UV Protection ? Protects your lens against dust, dirt & knocks ? Made in the USA ? 10 Year Warranty Box Contains ? 1 Filter ? 1 Filter brochure

productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Tiffen 55mm UV Protector Filter is a general use, clear filter that helps to absorb ultraviolet light and reduce the bluish cast of daylight. This filter is especially useful when photographing at high altitudes or around bodies of water. Filters help to reduce dust and moisture from reaching your lens element and provide additional protection in case of drops or situations where scratching could occur.Tiffen filters are made using ColorCore technology; a process that involves laminating the filter substrate between 2 pieces of optical glass, grinding flat to a tolerance of 1/10,000th of an inch, then mounting to precision metal rings.Absorbs some ultraviolet light and reduces bluish cast of daylight.Clear filter provides no additional coloration or contrast, allowing you to pair this filter with others.General protection filter reduces dust, moisture, and scratches from reaching lens elements.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Vanguard BIIN 37  Camera Bag(Green)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Whether you are a pro or an amateur photographer, you will want to carry your photography paraphernalia wherever you go. So carry and store your DSLR camera with style and practicality with this camera bag from Vanguard. Material The interior of this sling-style camera bag is made of 100 x 150D polyester and velvet that ensures the safety and security of your DSLR camera and other accessories. The outer layer is made of 150D polyester ripstop and 600 x 600D polyester that ensure its sturdiness and durability. Separate Compartments With separate compartments and a compact design, it cleverly divides interiors that can accommodate every accessory independently. It also provides a direct access to the top compartment through a separate zipper without having to open the bag completely. Capacity This camera bag can hold a DSLR camera with standard lens, 1-2 extra lenses, flash unit and memory cards, cables, battery and charger, water bottles and lens cap. For those who are looking for a compact yet an efficient camera bag, this shoulder bag could be a great choice. Padded Strap The thick padded strap feels comfortable on your shoulder even when you are carrying too many things. It has a metal ring on the strap which allows you to attach a small accessory or bag when required. The waist clip lets you secure the bag tightly against your waist whenever necessary. There are additional zipper pockets that can be used for storing lens caps and lens filters. Sling-style Bag This sling-style bag can be worn over one shoulder and easily rotated to the front to gain access to the camera. It is perfectly designed to be toted everywhere, providing instant access to your gear.
